ility of expert advice in times of need. My\npurpose in this essay is to explain why this view of the events of the trial is\nmisguided, however well intentioned, and misinformed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Nov 2012 01:17:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-15"}
