rt of SZpack should be\nuseful for analyzing high-resolution SZ data and computing SZ maps from\nsimulated clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Nov 2012 04:50:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Feb 2013 21:01:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
