ee by about 10 sigma in Vsin(i) for large spin-orbit\nmisalignments. It is thus important to apply the adapted model when fitting\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Nov 2012 14:18:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
